text: Kylie Fausto Verzosa (born February 7, 1992) is a Filipino actress, model and miss International 2016. Verzosa was born in the city of Baguio, Philippines. She finished from Manila Athenaeum University with a Bachelor of Business Administration and worked as a teacher. She become a member of the Professional Models Association of the Philippines. Verzosa took part at Miss International 2016 in Japan where she was won the crown of Miss International 2016.
